{"tid":1613090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛回家] 既編劇同導演實力 係金馬獎級數","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T12:07:33.000Z","uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"14d15165c1d250607179907993e29102117fabd2","tid":1613090,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"首先一集由8點至8點30分 <br />\n減埋主題曲+中間廣告時段 一集內容得20分鐘 重少過我每日睇AV既時間<br />\n20分鐘要講一個故事起承轉合 + 大眾睇得開心  編劇同導演實力深不可測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比個例子大家 世界第一既海賊王尾田榮一郎 20分鐘先講到8頁漫畫 但搵咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內容又要新又要老少咸宜 大大話幾百集到時今時今日都重比到新意大家<br />\n有冇連登手足可以提名佢地參加金馬獎 還咁有才華既編劇同導演實力一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f482ce8d8788df10d1881fb717b6bd9674bdd88","tid":1613090,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又想殺人"},{"pid":"a7196872652c293a0c2480d79cf22521adfb8285","tid":1613090,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"dislike cctvb thz"},{"pid":"7ed09c102f57727cdceb6c03f906f9a231d57370","tid":1613090,"uid":327789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"cctvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6443a70bd9264ef2219be058a4353f12082c36c","tid":1613090,"uid":81627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:42.000Z","msg":